<section id="frameworks" class="px-6 py-20 md:py-28 border-t border-border scroll-mt-20">
	<div class="mx-auto max-w-5xl">
		<p class="eyebrow text-center">Integrations</p>
		<h2 class="heading-lg text-center mt-3">Drop into any framework.<br/><span class="gradient-text-accent">Zero config.</span></h2>
		<p class="body-lg text-center max-w-2xl mx-auto mt-4">
			One plugin. 9 files. Every AI engine covered. No other AEO tool integrates with your build.
		</p>

		<!-- Framework logo grid -->
		<div class="flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-3 mt-14 stagger-children">
